text:
@HamdanMohammed 
@faz3
Happy birthday in advance! I'm so grateful to have you in my life. Your birthday is coming up, and I'm ready to celebrate the amazing person you are. You deserve more than one day of importance, so I'm starting early.
Only the most great people deserve their birthday wishes early, so happy birthday to you and may the countdown begin!
Happy advance birthday to the most amazing friend! I hope your day is filled with joy, and I can't wait to celebrate with you soon
